{"tid":2336471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"崩潰！497萬「最強奶媽」IG追蹤數瞬間歸零　謝薇安：別整我","createTime":"2020-12-22T15:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T23:55:53.000Z","uid":244704,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a73138bf1744eb2c2ac3ba67cc80996a652703f4","tid":2336471,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n自直播界跨足推出寫真書爆紅的直播主謝薇安（Vivian），外型高挑上圍更超豐滿，由於經常在個人社群網站Instagram放送豪乳裸照，吸引高達497萬人的驚人追蹤數，由於是單親媽媽，在於粉絲圈還有「最強奶媽」之稱，然而就在今（22號）謝薇安的IG帳號先是無預警登出，緊接著竟遭刪除，讓她崩潰直喊：「不要整我好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/22/2948990-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F2948990-PH.jpg&h=803d255b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼「最強奶媽」謝薇安因不吝於曬豪乳裸照，讓她飆出高人氣。（圖／翻攝自謝薇安臉書）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/22/2948945-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F2948945-PH.jpg&h=6fc588f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她經營IG 3年多的時間，突然Instagram被停用，謝薇安直言：「我也不知道發生了甚麼，該怎麼辦？」她表示自己剛要發一則玩具開箱限動，下一秒就跳登出畫面，讓她痛苦喊「2020年底了，還給我出個大事，不要整我好嗎&hellip;？ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/22/2948936-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F2948936-PH.jpg&h=82bf0779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲謝薇安今凌晨發現IG遭登出並無預警移除。（圖／翻攝自謝薇安臉書）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/22/2948937-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F2948937-PH.jpg&h=4331d8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲謝薇安IG遭無預警登出，接著帳號顯示被停用。（圖／翻攝自謝薇安臉書）<br />\n<br />\n謝薇安感性說到自己很珍惜經營的帳號，早期還有不少小孩嬰兒時期的照片，然而一夕之間卻化為烏有「一路從0到快要500萬了，每天每天留言努力回復 。」求助無門的她，目前已經循正常管道問IG官方，並拜託大家幫忙Tag帳號「讓官方可以注意到這件事情。」目前她不少業配工作已受影響，只得暫時先喊卡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.setn.com/news/869686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F869686&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=0db7cc5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F869686&h=1a53fd68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.setn.com/news/869686</a>"},{"pid":"84c765438b702220fba9c3053f9b1e8828a1b7eb","tid":2336471,"uid":66378,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"別怕，還有奶"},{"pid":"1e978f045b1a4b2a0a4f15d71d4f48a14b2290c1","tid":2336471,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"裸照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d302f0aeb618f65f544e7c378a122cec36fbf87","tid":2336471,"uid":154255,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"認真，雞嚟啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲女唔對波上枱面有撚人睇咩<br />\n全部都係露波露腳露pat<br />\n佢做到Billie Eilish 咁就話叻啫"},{"pid":"f1348f6e7c8fb954ea5963729d3ecfc652cc4eaa","tid":2336471,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed86c8acfcf8840766062c30af9fbab57f62b7b","tid":2336471,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c59b32fd6e36d747b6d0e7cc7a641d6078c2081","tid":2336471,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"